<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, wir <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz ir
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wellet, daz
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt und auch ir hab und
                                <expan>kawffmansch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und die iren
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> in
                            <expan>Nördling<ex>er</ex></expan> markt und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> darawsz durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                                <expan>burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>rschaft</expan> und gepiet <expan>sich<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        geleytet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, wenn sie
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> die iren <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        des <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Als etc. Das wellen etc. Und lat uns
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey disem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
